Name: AccountTimeZoneId
Notes: Name of the timezone. For example: "(GMT-05:00) Eastern Time".

Name: ClickType
Notes: Prevents zero-impression rows from being returned. The Impressions field will reflect how often the ad was served with that click type available. Since ads can serve with multiple click types displayed, impressions may be double counted and the totals may not be accurate.

Name: ConversionCategoryName
Notes: Not compatible with non-conversion stats (AverageCpc, Clicks, etc). Prevents zero-conversion rows from being returned.  Values: "Other", "View of a key page", "Purchase/Sale", "Signup", "Lead"

Name: ConversionRate
Notes: Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ConversionRateManyPerClick
Notes: Percentage returned as "x.xx%".

Name: ConversionTypeName
Notes: Not compatible with non-conversion stats (AverageCpc, Clicks, etc).  Prevents zero-conversion rows from being returned.

Name: ConversionValue
Notes: The HTTP header returnMoneyInMicros does not affect this field.

Name: CriteriaDestinationUrl
Notes: In the Destination URL report, this field behaves as a segment.

Name: CriteriaParameters
Notes: In the Destination URL report, this field behaves as a segment.

Name: CriteriaStatus
Notes: In the Destination URL report, this field behaves as a segment.

Name: Ctr
Notes: Percentage returned as "x.xx%".
